      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study conducted on the nominal pump geometry (3.1 M, 7.8 M, and 19.4 M cells). GCI for normalized hemolysis index is 2.8% between medium and fine meshes. Production mesh is the medium mesh. GCI criterion satisfied."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
