      "rationale": "In-vitro test loop conditions (flow rate, rotational speed, fluid temperature, hematocrit) were logged at 10 Hz and compared to CFD boundary conditions. All five operating points fall within ±3.1% of nominal. Test conditions requirement satisfied."
