      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) must agree with experimental values to within ±15% across all five operating points.",
      "rationale": "CFD-predicted NIH values compared against experimental measurements across five operating points. Maximum deviation is 11.4% at the 6 L/min, 3500 RPM condition. Mean absolute error is 7.2%. Acceptance criterion satisfied for all points."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
