      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, formal characterization of test sample variability is not required; lot traceability of bovine blood is sufficient.",
      "rationale": "Bovine blood sourced from a single certified lot (Lot BV-2024-117) used across all five validation experiments. Hematocrit verified at ±1% per ASTM F1841. Formal inter-sample variability analysis not required at MRL 2. Factor recorded as not-assessed."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
