      "acceptanceCriteria": "Input parameters used in validation simulations must be demonstrably equivalent to those used in the COU simulations within stated tolerances.",
      "rationale": "A parameter equivalency table was prepared comparing validation and COU simulation inputs across all 14 input categories. Fluid properties, rotational speed, flow rates, and hemolysis model constants are identical. Geometric fidelity confirmed by overlay of CMM and CAD surfaces with maximum deviation of 0.03 mm. Equivalency criterion satisfied."
